---
title: Warm Chicken, Apple & Kale Grain Bowls with Feta, Dried Cranberries, Almonds & Balsamic Vinaigrette
description: Step aside, simple side salads—this hearty kale and grain bowl deserves center stage! We mix crisp kale with a warm grain blend of whole-grain rice, bulgur, and barley. Add in crunchy apple, briny feta, chewy dried cranberries, then toss it all in a tangy-sweet honey Dijon balsamic vinaigrette. Top your bowls with juicy seared chicken cutlets for a light but hearty dinner you’re going to want to make again and again.
